						<summary>

						<p>On the east wall of the rock-cut shrine in the Mēlaikōyil temple.</p>						

						<p>.... varman. Year 12.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records the gift of 10 <hi rend="italic">tuḷaippoṉ</hi> by Pāṇḍiyadiyaraśi <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Pāṭṭam-Paḍāri for feeding 20 Brāhmaṇas daily during the seven days of Paṅguṉi-Uttiram.</p>						

